metadata.description:
Togetherness is a collection of 1 of 1 art, inspired by hyperconnectivity, and the different ways we are tied together and coexist in our communities. 

These paintings explore connection and identity experienced through shape and color as abstract versions of ourselves. Each piece takes twists and turns in bursts of new colors, yet remain in harmony, in conversation with one another.
